precis:
Enactment of the DEFINITION OF "WIRELESS TRANSMISSION SYSTEM" REGULATIONS
which, in defining this expression, will facilitate the task assigned to
the Copyright Board to set the special, transitional royalty to be paid for
the broadcasting of an artist's performance of a musical work or a sound
recording thereof.
